group.description:
Hemostasis 12 hours following surgery;
IB1001 Bolus Regimen: 120 IU/kg prior to start of procedure, followed by 60 IU/kg 12 hours after the first infusion, and up to 120 IU/kg 24 hours after the first infusion. Bolus infusions would continue every 12 hours for a minimum of 3 days; or
IB1001 Continuous Infusion Regimen: IB1001 infused at a target range of 70% to 110% for a minimum of 3 days post-procedure.

